T1  - Introduction to Special Topic Forum Influencing Politics and Political Systems: Political Systems and Corporate Strategies
AU  - Pearce, Jone L.
AU  - De Castro, Julio O.
AU  - Guillén, Mauro F.
Y1  - 2008/04/01
PY  - 2008
DA  - 2008/04/01
